	<h2>Welcome to EZRSS</h2>
	<div class="box padding">
		What is this?<br />
		EZRSS is a rss feed for <a href="http://eztv.it/" target="_blank">eztv</a>.<br />
		You can use it to have your bittorrent client download your favourite shows from eztv as they get<br />
		released, rather than having to stay up all night waiting for them - completely automatically.<br />
		<br />
		For more information about what rss is and how you can use it, see the <a href="/faq/">faq</a>.<br />
		<br />
		To show how simple the system is, just type the name of a show you would like to find:<br />
		<form method="get" action="/search/">
